      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-cared for by its previous owner. Mechanically, it runs smoothly with a strong engine and a responsive transmission that shifts as it should. The exterior is clean with only minor stone chips and light surface scratches consistent with normal use, while the interior is tidy and free of any major stains or tears. It has a complete service history and is ready for its next owner to drive away with confidence. This is a solid, dependable car that offers a great balance of quality and value.",
