      "description": "Hey there! You honestly won't find another one like this. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, kept in a climate-controlled garage and pampered since day one. It looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014not a single scratch or speck of dust anywhere! I'm sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to fall in love with it. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
