    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade E46 M3 in impeccable condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double VANOS timing. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual and a 25% locking limited-slip differential. Mechanically flawless, this vehicle has undergone proactive rod bearing replacement and comprehensive rear subframe reinforcement. The suspension geometry remains precise, with factory-spec bushings and dampers providing telepathic feedback. A true 'mint' specimen for the discerning enthusiast seeking peak longitudinal and lateral performance.",
