      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, meticulously maintained to meet the highest standards of a discerning collector. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections; it has been kept under a breathable cover in a climate-controlled garage since day one. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom state\u2014the premium leather retains its original scent and supple texture, with no creasing on the bolsters and pristine carpeting protected by original floor mats. Mechanically, the car is flawless, backed by a comprehensive service portfolio documenting every fluid change and inspection performed ahead of schedule. From the factory-spec engine bay to the spotless undercarriage, every detail reflects a life of pampered ownership. This is not just a used car; it is a preserved piece of automotive excellence ready for its next caretaker.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
